The Battle of Algiers ni filimi   yakinwe n'abataliyani bafatanyije n'abanyalijeliya yakinwe muri 1966 ivuga kumateka  yanditswe na iyoborwa Gillo Pontecorvo na Star Jean Martin na Saadi Yacef<ref>The Battle of Algiers | film by Pontecorvo [1966] | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › ... › Movies</ref> . Ishingiye ku bikorwa byakozwe n’inyeshyamba mu gihe cy’intambara ya Alijeriya (1954–1962) kurwanya leta y’Ubufaransa muri Afurika y’Amajyaruguru, icyagaragaye cyane ni Intambara izwi ku izina rya Algiers, umurwa mukuru wa Alijeriya<ref>The Battle of Algiers (1966) | The Criterion Collection <nowiki>https://www.criterion.com</nowiki> › films › 248-the-battle-of-al...</ref>. Yafatiwe amashusho ahantu  hateguwe na Roberto Rossellinimu buryo bwa  newsreel style: umwirabura n'umuzungu hamwe no guhindura ubwoko bwa documentaire kugirango hongerwe kumyumvire yukuri kwamateka, hamwe nabakinnyi badafite umwuga babayeho kurugamba nyarwo<ref>The Battle of Algiers movie review (1968) | Roger Ebert <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › the-battle-of-al...</ref>. Amanota ya film yahimbwe na Ennio Morricone . Bikunze guhuzwa na cinema yo mubutaliyani<ref>The Battle of Algiers - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › the_battle_of_algiers</ref>. 

Iyi filime yibanze cyane cyane ku barwanyi b'impinduramatwara Ali La Pointe mu myaka iri hagati ya 1954 na 1957, igihe abarwanyi b'inyeshyamba za FLN bishyira hamwe bakaguka i Casbah, umurwa mukuru wa Alijeriya<ref>Marc Lafia and Fang-Yu Lin: The Battle Of Algiers - Whitney ... <nowiki>https://whitney.org</nowiki> › exhibitions › battle-of-algiers</ref>. Ibikorwa byabo byahuye nabaparakomando b'Abafaransa bagerageza kugarura akarere kari karafashwe. Filime cyane ivuga kubyerekeye imitwe yitwara gisirikari hamwe nuburyo butemewe, nkiyicarubozo, byakoreshwaga nimbaraga zabakoloni  . Alijeriya yashoboye kubona ubwigenge bw'Abafaransa<ref>Terrorism on Screen: Lessons from The Battle of Algiers <nowiki>https://www.historians.org</nowiki> › october-2010 › terrorism-o...</ref>. 

Filime yarashimiwe cyane. Imitwe yombi y'inyeshyamba hamwe n'abayobozi ba leta basanze ari ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku ntambara yo mu mujyi <ref>The Battle of Algiers at Fifty | Film Quarterly <nowiki>https://filmquarterly.org</nowiki> › 2017/01/10 › the-battle-of-al...</ref>. Ifite umwanya wa 48 kuri ''Filime 250 za Critics ''' ''Amajwi ya Sight &amp;amp; Sound'' 2012<ref>The Battle of Algiers (La Battaglia di Algeri) - University of ... <nowiki>https://www.nottingham.ac.uk</nowiki> › film-rev-oct-2007</ref>,  ndetse n’umwanya wa 120 ku ''rutonde rw’ikinyamakuru Empire'' ku rutonde rwa "Filime 500 zikomeye mu bihe byose<ref>The Battle of Algiers | film by Pontecorvo [1966] | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › ... › Movies</ref>".  Yatoranijwe kugirango yinjire kurutonde rwa " Filime 100 zo mu Butaliyani zigomba gukizwa ". Ikibazo kijyanye na sociopolitiki, film ntabwo imaze imyaka itanu yerekanwe mubufaransa 1971. <ref>[http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/13698010701618604#.Uv4UbXeZh1w "The Illegitimate Legitimacy of the Battle of Algiers in French Film Culture", Patricia Caillé, ''Interventions: International Journal of Postcolonial Studies'' Volume 9, Issue 3, 2007 Special Issue: Gillo Pontecorvo's Battle of Algiers, 40 Years On]</ref>
